ing these input elements maintain visual consistency with the existing design language. I've integrated these elements to seamlessly fit within the modal's layout, maintaining proper spacing and responsiveness. I am paying close attention to the visual hierarchy of these latest additions.\n\n\n**Finalizing the UI Elements**\n\nI've just styled the document visibility dropdown, integrating it seamlessly into the upload modal with consistent styling. I've used similar classes and properties as other fields to maintain a cohesive look, using `font-bold` for emphasis. I am also working on adding a description summary field, ensuring proper visual hierarchy.\n\n\n**Styling the Buttons**\n\nNow I'm focusing on the cancel and submit buttons in the modal. I've ensured a cohesive visual style by using rounded borders, appropriate padding, and hover effects that enhance user interaction, and implemented the appropriate states for both. I am paying close attention to disabled states as well.\n\n\n"}}
